{"tid":2143020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國最高法院：僱主可因宗教信仰拒提供避孕醫療","createTime":"2020-08-06T23:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T23:59:14.000Z","uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf7693a46a0a06aa29f1137d6ad81ebe855f3b3","tid":2143020,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:21:21.000Z","msg":"最高法院8日以7票對2票表決結果通過裁定，僱主可基於宗教信仰理由，拒絕為員工提供醫療保險服務裡的避孕項目。華盛頓郵報報導，<span class=\"red\">根據政府報告估計，最高法院這項裁定將讓7萬名至12萬6000名之間的女性勞工，無法再取得免費的避孕醫療服務。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkxWnWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjkxWnWK.jpg&h=3c477dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前總統歐巴馬任內推出俗稱「歐記健保」的「可負擔健保法」(Affordable Care Act)，法律架構規定僱主提供的醫療保險計畫當中，女性員工可免費取得避孕服務項目，但教會、猶太教堂則擁有豁免權。<br />\n<br />\n川普總統上台後，行政部門頒布多項新規，希望把「歐記健保」避孕醫療服務豁免權的適用範圍擴大，不但非營利組織能夠涵蓋在適用範圍，就連營利事業也一體適用，從中小企業到「財富500強」(Fortune 500)榜上有名的公司都包括在內。<br />\n<br />\n根據最高法院裁定，川普政府得以允許僱主基於宗教信仰或道德信念因素，退出「歐記健保」當中的避孕服務條款。<span class=\"red\">不過，從女性勞工的角度來看，今後透過僱主醫療保險免費取得避孕服務，恐將受到諸多限制。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>宗教自由呢個真係一個好好用既理由</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797f9e3958a54c903bf9687af9e101437bb7e56a","tid":2143020,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"7:2<br />\n連自由派嘅大法官都倒戈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3107bd6c1b762a93fb5cdd30163d9278a23f522","tid":2143020,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"797f9e3958a54c903bf9687af9e101437bb7e56a","tid":2143020,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:35:16.000Z","msg":"7:2<br />\n連自由派嘅大法官都倒戈呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:37:53.000Z","msg":"保守派就因為佢地啲傳統文化價值觀當然支持，自由派就因為所謂既宗教自由傾向支持，即使係明顯on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189cb5516a1d0e9b97e4d8617df95ed6f0a1de76","tid":2143020,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:44:06.000Z","msg":"一個月前新聞你貼黎做咩"},{"pid":"a657f9d448a24df305afa2c70621f519433cb373","tid":2143020,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"189cb5516a1d0e9b97e4d8617df95ed6f0a1de76","tid":2143020,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:44:06.000Z","msg":"一個月前新聞你貼黎做咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:48:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔幾個月前既都貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講都無見到其他連仔有講過呢樣野，一個月又唔係咩好耐既事，件事仲好新"},{"pid":"094ed891481982f90d2edb2676df189db835f241","tid":2143020,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a657f9d448a24df305afa2c70621f519433cb373","tid":2143020,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"189cb5516a1d0e9b97e4d8617df95ed6f0a1de76","tid":2143020,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:44:06.000Z","msg":"一個月前新聞你貼黎做咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:48:24.000Z","msg":"連登仔幾個月前既都貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講都無見到其他連仔有講過呢樣野，一個月又唔係咩好耐既事，件事仲好新"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T23:54:30.000Z","msg":"咁就唔知你用意係咩<br />\n不過如果你想話保守派已經得勢喇喎<br />\n可以睇下Pence點解開火屌鳩John Roberts"},{"pid":"66f18b595886a59ea0c34119c36633bcac8c10a2","tid":2143020,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"094ed891481982f90d2edb2676df189db